<p>Our goal is to ensure that specific and achievable requirements are defined - we seek to be purposeful and specific when it comes to information requirements.</p>
<p>Each <strong>purpose</strong> (why) will be <strong>described</strong> for an <strong>Information Delivery Milestone</strong> along with start/finish dates (when) and a list of all <strong>objects</strong> (what) that are required.&nbsp;</p>
<p>The Level of Information Need (how) will be captured in the <strong>Scope grid</strong> with:</p>
<ol>
<li>Geometrical Information</li>
<li>Alphanumerical Information&nbsp;</li>
<li>and Documentation r<span style="color: rgb(95, 95, 95); font-family: &quot;Open sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">equirements</span>
</li>
